  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing national and sub-national capacities to prepare learners for peace and sustainable development challenges in South Asia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SDG4.7 is a foundation of the SDG4 as a transformative agenda. UNESCO New Delhi in collaboration with the key partners like MGIEP and APCEIU will assist countries in the sub-region to integrate core values of SDG4.7 into their national education policies, teacher education, curriculum and assessment. Support will be provided to improve pre-service teacher education aiming to integrate these values in teacher education. In the area of Education for health and wellbeing education, UNESCO New Delhi will build on the experiences of work undertaken in the Indian States of Tamil Nadu and Gujarat and support State Education Departments in rolling out policy and programmes to eliminate and prevent School-related Gender-based Violence and the creation of safe and inclusive education environments.</narrative>
  </description>
